@Zerg: With money you do get something you can trust in. After all, the ones responsible for it are elected to do so by you. If you cannot trust them, the problem isn't with the currency but with how they are elected. 

If you really wish to get something physical in exchange for what you earn, which is fairly stable, you can always _buy_ gold. 

Sorry for the split comments, I'm just not used to it automatically posting on enter. :)
